Title: Read press announcement title and answer a survey about company's business strategy
Description: ONLY need to read the TITLEs of the press announcement by 396 companies on NASDAQ and NYSE and answer the survey whether the companies adopt any of the 3 business strategy  (i.e. analytics, innovation, technology). Common sense can also be used.
Keywords: business news, text analysis, business strategy
